","text":"Optional parameters you’d like to pass with your placement. These can be referenced within the rules"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of your campaign. Keys beginning with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"$"},{"type":"text","text":" are reserved for Superwall and will be dropped. Values can be any"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"JSON encodable value, URLs or Dates. Arrays and dictionaries as values are not supported at this time, and will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be dropped."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"params"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An optional ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit\/PaywallOverrides","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" object whose parameters override the paywall defaults. Use this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to override products and whether it ignores the subscription status. Defaults to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}],"name":"paywallOverrides"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An optional completion block that gets called when the paywall should dismiss. This defaults to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":" and the SDK","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"will call ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"presentationMode.wrappedValue.dismiss()"},{"text":" by default. Otherwise you must perform the dismissal of the paywall.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"onRequestDismiss"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A completion block that accepts an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Error"},{"type":"text","text":" and returns a "},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". This will show when the requested"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"paywall is skipped. Defaults to ","type":"text"},{"code":"EmptyView()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"onErrorView"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A completion block containing a feature that you wish to paywall. Access to this block is remotely configurable via the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/superwall.com\/dashboard"},{"type":"text","text":". If the paywall is set to "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Non Gated"}]},{"type":"text","text":", this will be called when"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the paywall is dismissed or if the user is already paying. If the paywall is "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Gated"}]},{"type":"text","text":", this will be called only if the user is already paying"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or if they begin paying. If no paywall is configured, this gets called immediately. This will not be called in the event of an error."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"feature"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This uses ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Superwall\/getPaywall(forPlacement:params:paywallOverrides:delegate:)"},{"text":" under the hood.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"aside","name":"Warning","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You’re responsible for the deallocation of this view. If you have a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallView"},{"type":"text","text":" presented somewhere"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and you try to present the same "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallView"},{"type":"text","text":" elsewhere, you will get a crash."}]}],"style":"warning"}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A SwiftUI paywall view that you can embed into your app."}],"references":{